{"tid":91414,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人的自我修養","createTime":"2017-01-22T23:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T02:19:00.000Z","uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c32f08c835912a5b9ea0156a6916c0f5a197e951","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T23:50:15.000Z","msg":"話說開頭<br />\n<br />\n首先我想講<br />\n<br />\n窮人係必須要存在起呢個世上<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁撚幼稚講埋d乜撚滅貧<br />\n<br />\n就算一班窮人脫左貧<br />\n<br />\n佢地只係踩到另一班窮人更加窮"},{"pid":"22f10bca9b6360a8d799ba67dbb22617c4858e9c","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T23:59:37.000Z","msg":"窮人首先要做既<br />\n<br />\n就係反省一下點解你咁窮<br />\n<br />\n好多窮人以為自己既窮係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 其他人害佢<br />\n<br />\n2. 懷才不遇<br />\n<br />\n3. 機會仲未出現<br />\n<br />\n4. 社會不公平<br />\n<br />\n我話你知，95%既窮人窮既原因都係因為你廢。廢可以係學歷低（例如ive），蠢，懶，心態錯。"},{"pid":"e417ac35642c87a7b703130ed02e5ee72305e5d8","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:02:49.000Z","msg":"窮人成日怨無錢<br />\n<br />\n但點解你唔諗下你係自食其果？<br />\n<br />\n你廢，所以窮。你窮，所以生活差<br />\n<br />\n你廢，你既生活差，其實係好理所當然"},{"pid":"5e6bbb054bac58639126c48b4154d09c9e744242","tid":91414,"uid":68986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:04:21.000Z","msg":"任何國家都有窮人 我既睇法係需要有窮人去做野 清潔 運輸 建築等去幫個社會運行 而社會大部分人係金字塔低層 流動機會越上越窄 曾經夢想係有一個公平 大家都有機會上流 人人開心社會 而家諗起覺得好幼稚 生存就已經拼盡全力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c24895d9fc964af3ed48d6e2b94b207a3715ed9","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>任何國家都有窮人 我既睇法係需要有窮人去做野 清潔 運輸 建築等去幫個社會運行 而社會大部分人係金字塔低層 流動機會越上越窄 曾經夢想係有一個公平 大家都有機會上流 人人開心社會 而家諗起覺得好幼稚 生存就已經拼盡全力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正確"},{"pid":"341fd63141be4bcbb7644748f29af19af775d24a","tid":91414,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:06:38.000Z","msg":"多數都係縮窄貧富差距，好少聽人講話要滅貧，打稻草人？"},{"pid":"8de99339147b4c09b676a2893e4c3242eb85fa9b","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多數都係縮窄貧富差距，好少聽人講話要滅貧，打稻草人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大愛撚會成日講，好幼稚"},{"pid":"3b34c6e9aebad995cb48293b50e4bbaf2acea6c9","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:21:39.000Z","msg":"既然你'窮'呢個結果係理所當然<br />\n<br />\n窮人如果又唔認自己廢，又或者無能力去改變自己既廢，可以點？我稱呼呢d為永久性窮人<br />\n<br />\n以下就列出永久性窮人應有既心態：<br />\n<br />\n1. 得閒買兩件你心目中既所謂名牌包裝自己，話比人知你唔窮，影相放上fb。<br />\n<br />\n2. 日日妙想天開中六合彩突然發達。賭波馬，以為自己勁過精算師。<br />\n<br />\n3. 大大聲鳩叫，呢個社會好唔公平呀！我窮係因為比人打壓呀！<br />\n<br />\n4. 好留意有d乜野大減價即刻狗衝去買，尤其是心中所謂既名牌。<br />\n<br />\n5. 平時食飯搭車慳得就慳，見人既地方就扮光鮮。"},{"pid":"411bcd82fdae96ad1a8d6a830a072241bd1bd49b","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:28:50.000Z","msg":"永久性窮人首先應該接受你自己既窮。<br />\n<br />\n用短缺既金錢去偽裝成有錢人。<br />\n<br />\n推動你去面對未來係你中六合彩既幻想。<br />\n<br />\n鳩叫世界不公平去平衡你既心態。<br />\n<br />\n當有日，你真心話比人知金錢係萬惡既，你成功了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ebdb81708a94eff1a83109f999f3fc618baa13","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cad2cee5632061ae0b870c5b1cbe97a7c1b532b","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fa39ab3d9164f46536d6e72635538e9696d898","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9e98acab9b7ece8e3e7d7ad6836ec7810a0a3f","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81d1bcbc0fc48f271b55be114c7acf5b045d50e","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb609faac67775fb21d1b630c3c4d2717bdb39df","tid":91414,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:49:11.000Z","msg":"又真＿|￣|<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634ff28abf9122bf8169d270cd52ca32e094be22","tid":91414,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:55:23.000Z","msg":"好mean但真"},{"pid":"f852953a813436762cc54657615aadfaf23101d5","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9babedf69f6e71e7259b83ea85328ddb967458a5","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207d9b68541be630b2e437c6834b4d08881354a3","tid":91414,"uid":4158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"好屈機"},{"pid":"b92b8128035431d2b90c3143de58aa895c7d8fae","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205b8d7695fbac9a8339d9ccba4025579c6b276b","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"點解大部份人都咁痛苦？<br />\n<br />\n因為你以爲自己可以更好<br />\n<br />\n港女話齊：<br />\n<br />\nThe best is yet to come<br />\n<br />\n但首先要注意<br />\n<br />\n你憑乜野去得到更好既生活？"},{"pid":"fb411aa