\n<br />\n成功需父幹<br />\n<br />\n如果樓主出身底層，一早收左皮啦，仲係度以為看透世事咁教訓人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮人生活都可以好開心<br />\n<br />\n本topic 想講既自我修養係想講呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n未入正題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮人都可以開心<br />\n<br />\n你係窮人咩<br />\n你試過日日為錢煩未<br />\n你個靠老豆既廢柴2世祖有咩資格講呢d"},{"pid":"abd5e6692c5cc5972190f893b7d0850999c49387","tid":91414,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:01:32.000Z","msg":"鬥慘實驗係無論你幾窮幾有錢都好，只要你係個圈子裡唔係最慘一個。<br />\n你要係圈子裡找到個比你更慘既，否則你要立即離開呢個圈子。"},{"pid":"819a905c4a16ee54c3f3aae8325b6e6dd1aabe23","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"人生<br />\n<br />\n只不過求開心<br />\n<br />\n窮人都可以過得開心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/_LcXEpfLkxPQax2dR0khOP0zRw0rxd3kFHO3tPITrbspZQsAaoBVT01_rVcYorYwIc1k5xt92FJPXrSmKGxgrx3twcE=s0-d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh6.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F_LcXEpfLkxPQax2dR0khOP0zRw0rxd3kFHO3tPITrbspZQsAaoBVT01_rVcYorYwIc1k5xt92FJPXrSmKGxgrx3twcE%3Ds0-d&h=0914515a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79cd13cfd557c0b167dd411fcd5e166dbbce53e0","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>掉轉想，點先可以成功，有錢<br />\n<br />\n好似以樓主為例,住千幾萬既樓，有幾百萬cash, 點解咁勁?<br />\n<br />\n成功需父幹<br />\n<br />\n如果樓主出身底層，一早收左皮啦，仲係度以為看透世事咁教訓人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮人生活都可以好開心<br />\n<br />\n本topic 想講既自我修養係想講呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n未入正題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮人都可以開心<br />\n<br />\n你係窮人咩<br />\n你試過日日為錢煩未<br />\n你個靠老豆既廢柴2世祖有咩資格講呢d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為錢煩因為係製造左用錢既慾望"},{"pid":"5b5db93b4a12374405d763846f2e106e3c35931b","tid":91414,"uid":52283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"窮人特性個段真心唔錯"},{"pid":"f6feee2e4a3b0cacf8f27c8df7130949c1ef9ab4","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"