onder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人有時真係好撚on9, 月入高月月清個啲話自己窮咩心態，好似你條on9仔咁，懶係看破紅塵咁，月洗費當你2萬價值既物質，但真正既窮系連正常生存物質質素當你1萬都冇呀，個啲就真正窮。<br />\n<br />\n你屌緊個啲咩懷才不遇既on9仔話自己窮個d人既腦都on77啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70430c4a8398951147a8148cc7812c5520e66560","tid":91414,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:49:35.000Z","msg":"唔想再睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43984910ef9efc6b7c6037ea1be954e1acafcbd3","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T00:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a59e474c775b59b4d25bdd2cc6c15091efde66","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T00:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414d4060dc4f46217eeb4afb93ebd13c07fff192","tid":91414,"uid":44534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"講真屈機男係廢 又皮零野比人收皮 但中肯點講個post講野不無道理"},{"pid":"abe9bf806ed2a1b8473e90916328700f937fc9b4","tid":91414,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真屈機男係廢 又皮零野比人收皮 但中肯點講個post講野不無道理</blockquote><br />\n挑，佢屌緊啲心不足既人，唔係窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5100a6574c0a46723c8cb7325255ce0403231e3f","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,