34955fad","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"用'希望'呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n窮人就可以麻醉自己生存落去"},{"pid":"9050d3c13b0e98d854ddd06dbad327ad14ccc19d","tid":91414,"uid":36289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:11:13.000Z","msg":"以前會覺得d有錢人好仆街 好唔公平<br />\n但e加人大左，見多左人，會覺醒有d人係抵佢窮足一世，有d人係抵佢發，唔發反而覺得冇天理<br />\n又會覺得有d人將來一定有作為<br />\n利申 暫時睇人都幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5972a37fa692c8935e4505e35336bce26e490f6","tid":91414,"uid":13744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用'希望'呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n窮人就可以麻醉自己生存落去</blockquote><br />\n冇希望就唔會有動力<br />\n<br />\n冇動力就真係冇希望脫貧"},{"pid":"ecda3988e6e545a628a52bc94ccf657d08f8d279","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前會覺得d有錢人好仆街 好唔公平<br />\n但e加人大左，見多左人，會覺醒有d人係抵佢窮足一世，有d人係抵佢發，唔發反而覺得冇天理<br />\n又會覺得有d人將來一定有作為<br />\n利申 暫時睇人都幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你識得咁講已經睇到好通<br />\n<br />\n有d人有某d特質<br />\n<br />\n係會好易窮一世<br />\n<br />\n佢地憎人富貴<br />\n<br />\n眼中既有錢人都係大奸大惡<br />\n<br />\n但自己又成日幻想有一日個天會跌個機會來令自己發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8d21a1b328cb5d236c7c3ba5b49851c4a03745","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用'希望'呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n窮人就可以麻醉自己生存落去</blockquote><br />\n冇希望就唔會有動力<br />\n<br />\n冇動力就真係冇希望脫貧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時候窮人眼中既'希望'<br />\n<br />\n其實只係幻想，成功率億份之一<br />\n<br />\n例如中六合彩<br />\n<br />\n而有發達潛力既人眼中既希望<br />\n<br />\n成功率高好多<br />\n<br />\n有踏實既計劃，破釜沉舟既心<br />\n<br />\n就算本來成功率唔高<br />\n<br />\n都以自己能力去達成目標"},{"pid":"bba5bd647688430178fea9a2223519941cb1605d","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab368d4f3362e8ce9b8ae8f3d045a933a1a2484","tid":91414,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"雖然屈機男講嘢係仆街啲 但都有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42bd806440330b4f81c5d7ce477ee5f88b65401","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然屈機男講嘢係仆街啲 但都有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n忠言，逆耳<br />\n<br />\n我講真話<br />\n<br />\n好多廢人反駁唔到就一味鳩屌<br />\n<br />\n因為觸動到佢地窮人玻璃心"},{"pid":"168b6f099c143c7ef8862bf72a2b5551a4f5c8e8","tid":91414,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uM9H6GCzKkA \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuM9H6GCzKkA%20&d=uJJZkqHGH4AVduFxQmeqIgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=eac2fd9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uM9H6GCzKkA </a>"},{"pid":"d66ed19f1bd9201577cc1aef8a8de090415ec164","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/uM9H6GCzKkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuM9H6GCzKkA&d=uJJZkqHGH4AVduFxQmeqIgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6cffbca5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uM9H6GCzKkA</a> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n難聽<br />\n<br />\n但有邊句係假？"},{"pid":"87c2d165597e2aa7a890ae9fd87f07335a1d505b","tid":91414,"uid":36289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然屈機男講嘢係仆街啲 但都有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hk