率億份之一<br />\n<br />\n例如中六合彩<br />\n<br />\n而有發達潛力既人眼中既希望<br />\n<br />\n成功率高好多<br />\n<br />\n有踏實既計劃，破釜沉舟既心<br />\n<br />\n就算本來成功率唔高<br />\n<br />\n都以自己能力去達成目標</blockquote><br />\n只限於大學學歷，你打溜左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca2216c15e7aeba21ac41291288f0ed42188af5","tid":91414,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用'希望'呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n窮人就可以麻醉自己生存落去</blockquote><br />\n冇希望就唔會有動力<br />\n<br />\n冇動力就真係冇希望脫貧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時候窮人眼中既'希望'<br />\n<br />\n其實只係幻想，成功率億份之一<br />\n<br />\n例如中六合彩<br />\n<br />\n而有發達潛力既人眼中既希望<br />\n<br />\n成功率高好多<br />\n<br />\n有踏實既計劃，破釜沉舟既心<br />\n<br />\n就算本來成功率唔高<br />\n<br />\n都以自己能力去達成目標</blockquote><br />\n只限於大學學歷，你打溜左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個連書都讀唔好既人，係冇叫雞男所講既特徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03db746f9e175dd40486463960ce769ad8edc2ed","tid":91414,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:25:37.000Z","msg":"低學歷同窮人應該安份守己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcaead8366da307e3a0cc83bc4a5240d3e44959","tid":91414,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用'希望'呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n窮人就可以麻醉自己生存落去</blockquote><br />\n所以六合彩，馬，波呢d 賭博必須存在起社會上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348b445c3c5db0dc3241dd82e717c11c2134d909","tid":91414,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}